Based on issue #12 

Filter out `NextKeyword` from the `search` return values which will be used by average users.
To get `NextKeyword`, an advanced user can use the `progress_callback`.

### Example:

```python
findex_interface.search_wrapper(["Mar"], msk, label, max_depth=0, progress_callback=p.progress_callback)

### ProgressCallback output ###
Progress at depth 0 : {'Mar': [NextKeyword(TWFydA==)]}

### Search output ###
Search result: {'Mar': []}
```

```python
res = findex_interface.search_wrapper(["Mar"], msk, label, max_depth=1, progress_callback=p.progress_callback)
print("Search result:", res)

### ProgressCallback output ###
Progress at depth 0 : {'Mar': [NextKeyword(TWFydA==)]}
Progress at depth 1 : {'Mart': [NextKeyword(TWFydGk=)]}

### Search output ###
Search result: {'Mar': []}
```

```python
res = findex_interface.search_wrapper(["Mar"], msk, label, max_depth=2, progress_callback=p.progress_callback)
print("Search result:", res)

### ProgressCallback output ###
Progress at depth 0 : {'Mar': [NextKeyword(TWFydA==)]}
Progress at depth 1 : {'Mart': [NextKeyword(TWFydGk=)]}
Progress at depth 2 : {'Marti': [NextKeyword(TWFydGlh), NextKeyword(TWFydGlu)]}

### Search output ###
Search result: {'Mar': []}
```

```python
res = findex_interface.search_wrapper(["Mar"], msk, label, max_depth=3, progress_callback=p.progress_callback)
print("Search result:", res)

### ProgressCallback output ###
Progress at depth 0 : {'Mar': [NextKeyword(TWFydA==)]}
Progress at depth 1 : {'Mart': [NextKeyword(TWFydGk=)]}
Progress at depth 2 : {'Marti': [NextKeyword(TWFydGlh), NextKeyword(TWFydGlu)]}
Progress at depth 3 : {'Martin': [Location(MQ==)], 'Martia': [NextKeyword(TWFydGlhbA==)]}

### Search output ###
Search result: {'Mar': [Location(MQ==)]}
```

```python
res = findex_interface.search_wrapper(["Mar"], msk, label, max_depth=4, progress_callback=p.progress_callback)
print("Search result:", res)

### ProgressCallback output ###
Progress at depth 0 : {'Mar': [NextKeyword(TWFydA==)]}
Progress at depth 1 : {'Mart': [NextKeyword(TWFydGk=)]}
Progress at depth 2 : {'Marti': [NextKeyword(TWFydGlu), NextKeyword(TWFydGlh)]}
Progress at depth 3 : {'Martin': [Location(MQ==)], 'Martia': [NextKeyword(TWFydGlhbA==)]}
Progress at depth 4 : {'Martial': [Location(Mg==)]}

### Search output ###
Search result: {'Mar': [Location(MQ==), Location(Mg==)]}
```
